name: Skechers Women's Uno - Night Shades Lace-Up Sneaker
reviews: These are the first pair of Skechers I've ever bought and I absolutely love them! The bright pink is just fabulous. I love these shoes. More than anything. I did buy a box of 20 different colors. Shoelaces and I put neon green in these and they are amazing. I'm probably going to buy all the colors! You won't regret buying these shoes. They're extremely comfortable, great to walk in and I've even jogged in them. Jogging probably isn't the best because they are kind of tall. I would say these shoes have a lift in them. They make me like an inch and a half taller than I really am. But they are extremely comfortable coming from somebody who's worn Saucony pretty much her entire adult life. Love these shoes. You won't regret it!
